-------------------------------------------------------------- |Other parties |3.5 |3.1 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |HNS |3.4 |5.9 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |SDP |3.3 |3.7 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |IDS |1.6 |4.5 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- The report also contains a table of the "reasons for citizens' dissatisfaction." The results are as follows: ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- | |Yes |No |Do not know | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- |-- Fall in standa-|about 81 |13.2 |4.9 | |rd of living | | | | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- |-- Occupation of |about 79 |14.8 |6.9 | |one quarter of th-| | | | |e country's terri-| | | | |tory | | | | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- |-- Crime and immo-|about 71 |20.8 |8.7 | |ral behavior of p-| | | | |oliticians | | | | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- |-- Economic situa-|about 56 |28 |16 | |tion | | | | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- |-- Leadership's l-|about 49 |30.6 |20.9 | |ack of ability | | | | -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
